      <title>hexo_matery_configure 记录</title>
      <link href="/2021/10/07/hexo-matery-configure/"/>
      <url>/2021/10/07/hexo-matery-configure/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1、新增menu-》Gallery显示中文"><a href="#1、新增menu-》Gallery显示中文" class="headerlink" title="1、新增menu-》Gallery显示中文"></a>1、新增menu-》Gallery显示中文</h2><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">1、站点文件_config.yml中menu下增加  Gallery:    url: /gallery2、主题下面的languages文件夹-》zh-CN.yml文件中增加   gallery: 相册3、文件./layout/_partial/navigation.ejs中增加   menuMap.set<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Gallery"</span>, <span class="token string">"相册"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre><h2 id="2、配置hexo-new-xxx-时默认产生的头部信息"><a href="#2、配置hexo-new-xxx-时默认产生的头部信息" class="headerlink" title="2、配置hexo new xxx 时默认产生的头部信息"></a>2、配置hexo new xxx 时默认产生的头部信息</h2><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">1、站点文件 ./scaffolds/post.md 中添加相关配置---<span class="token punctuation">..</span>.author: cyftags:categories:summary:password: f242ac52b603121f3d86906819b519a64567864b296797cf15f3a1342c1e8717img: img: /medias/featureimages/1.jpg---</code></pre><h2 id="3、-安装文章字数统计插件"><a href="#3、-安装文章字数统计插件" class="headerlink" title="3、 安装文章字数统计插件"></a>3、 安装文章字数统计插件</h2><h3 id="3-1、安装命令如下"><a href="#3-1、安装命令如下" class="headerlink" title="3.1、安装命令如下"></a>3.1、安装命令如下</h3><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> i --save hexo-wordcount</code></pre><h3 id="3-2、在主题下的-config-yml-文件中将各个文章字数相关的配置激活"><a href="#3-2、在主题下的-config-yml-文件中将各个文章字数相关的配置激活" class="headerlink" title="3.2、在主题下的 _config.yml 文件中将各个文章字数相关的配置激活"></a>3.2、在主题下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件中将各个文章字数相关的配置激活</h3><pre class=" language-yaml"><code class="language-yaml"><span class="token key atrule">postInfo</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>  <span class="token key atrule">date</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token boolean important">true </span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 发布日期</span>  <span class="token key atrule">update</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token boolean important">true </span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 更新日期</span>  <span class="token key atrule">wordCount</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token boolean important">true </span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 文章字数统计</span>  <span class="token key atrule">totalCount</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token boolean important">false </span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 站点总文章字数</span>  <span class="token key atrule">min2read</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token boolean important">true </span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 文章阅读时长</span>  <span class="token key atrule">readCount</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token boolean important">false </span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 文章阅读次数</span></code></pre><p><br/>结束</br></p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">万事无如退步人，孤云野鹤自由身；松风十里时来往，笑揖峰头月一轮。</code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
